  <h2><a href="node/69" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Free Course in Remixing Video with Free Software">Free Course in Remixing Video with Free Software</a></h2> 
   
  <p>This weekend, I will hold a course entitled "Editing and Remixing Video with Free Software" in cooperation with <a href="http://sensus.se">Sensus</a>, one of the many excellent adult education association in Sweden. Using the simple but powerful video editor <a href="http://kdenlive.org">Kdenlive</a>, the participants will learn how to legally use freely licensed material to create their own music videos. The course will take place over two full days and is free of charge.</p>
   
  <p class="info">Posted in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_1 first last"><a href="taxonomy/term/1" rel="tag" title="uncategorized">Uncategorized</a></li>
</ul> <ul class="links inline"><li class="blog_usernames_blog first"><a href="blog/5.3" title="Read julipan&#039;s latest blog entries.">julipan&#039;s blog</a></li>
<li class="node_read_more last"><a href="node/69" title="Read the rest of Free Course in Remixing Video with Free Software.">Read more</a></li>
</ul></p>
   <small>Submitted by julipan on Mon, 09/29/2008 - 21:51</small>
   
</div>

<hr class="low" /><div class="entry"> 
   
  <h2><a href="node/68" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to SOTD: The End of Free Communications?">SOTD: The End of Free Communications?</a></h2> 
   
  <p><a href="http://fscons.org/speakers/?action=speaker&amp;id=48">Oscar Swartz </a>teams up with the other speakers at <a href="../index.html">FSCONS</a>. Oscar will give a speech called <a href="http://fscons.org/events/?action=event&amp;id=50">The End of Free Communications?</a></p>
<p><em>I discuss initiatives to curtail free communications. I put the development in a broader cultural context where I see the Internet as undermining old authorities and hierarchies. The established powers respond by waging unwinnable wars against imagined enemies and ill-defined groups: "terrorists", "pirates" and "pedophiles".</em></p>
   
  <p class="info">Posted in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_1 first last"><a href="taxonomy/term/1" rel="tag" title="uncategorized">Uncategorized</a></li>
</ul> <ul class="links inline"><li class="blog_usernames_blog first"><a href="blog/6.3" title="Read hesa&#039;s latest blog entries.">hesa&#039;s blog</a></li>
<li class="node_read_more last"><a href="node/68" title="Read the rest of SOTD: The End of Free Communications?.">Read more</a></li>
</ul></p>
   <small>Submitted by hesa on Fri, 09/26/2008 - 11:44</small>
   
