  <h2><a href="node/64" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Interview with Johan Thelin on QT, Gtk and much more">Interview with Johan Thelin on QT, Gtk and much more</a></h2> 
   
  <p><a href="http://fscons.org/speakers/?action=speaker&amp;id=11">Johan Thelin</a> who is coming to FSCONS to give a talk called <a href="http://fscons.org/events/?action=event&amp;id=29">Qt for Embedded Linux</a> and also to present the <a href="http://fscons.org/events/?action=event&amp;id=45">QtCentre Contest Award</a> have been interviewed by the FSCONS team.</p>
<p>During the interview Johan shares his views on Free Software, Qt and Gtk, ubiquitous computing, eye candy and more.</p>
<p>Read the whole <a href="http://fscons.org/interview-with-johan-thelin/">interview with Johan Thelin</a></p>
   
