<hr class="low" /><div class="entry"> 
   
  <h2><a href="node/63" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to SOTD: Midgard">SOTD: Midgard</a></h2> 
   
  <p><a href="http://fscons.org/speakers/?action=speaker&amp;id=21">Henri Bergius</a><a> comes to FSCONS </a>to <a href="http://fscons.org/events/?action=event&amp;id=37">speak about Midgard</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Midgard,</strong> a venerable open source content management system is now renewing itself to a new architecture. The plan is to provide a data management framework that can extend from web services to replicated mobile applications.</p>
   
  <p class="info">Posted in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_1 first last"><a href="taxonomy/term/1" rel="tag" title="uncategorized">Uncategorized</a></li>
