  <h2><a href="node/62" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to SOTD: How far behind is free+open culture?">SOTD: How far behind is free+open culture?</a></h2> 
   
  <p><a href="http://fscons.org/speakers/?action=speaker&amp;id=51">Mike Linksvayer</a> <a href="http://fscons.org/speakers/?action=speaker&amp;id=51">(</a><a href="http://creativecommons.org/about/people#21">Vice President of Creative Commons</a>) is coming to FSCONS to give the talk <a href="http://fscons.org/events/?action=event&amp;id=53">How far behind is free+open culture?</a></p>
<p>Mike Linksvayer is <a href="http://creativecommons.org/about/people#21">Vice President of Creative Commons</a>, where he manages core programs and operations. He joined Creative Commons as <a href="http://creativecommons.org/weblog/entry/5383">CTO</a> in 2003.</p>
   
  <p class="info">Posted in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_1 first last"><a href="taxonomy/term/1" rel="tag" title="uncategorized">Uncategorized</a></li>
